definition.value: A N-arylpiperazine that is piperazine substituted by 2-(4-aminophenyl)ethyl and 3-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl groups at positions 1 and 4, respectively. It is a selective 5-HT1A serotonin receptor agonist and 5-HT1D serotonin receptor antagonist.
A 1-benzothiophene substituted by a 2-{4-[4-(pyrrolidin-1-yl)piperidine-1-carbonyl]anilino}pyrimidin-4-yl group at position 2. It is an IkappaB kinase (IKK) inhibitor.
